00:25:19.530 --> 00:25:22.860
[Moddang]: Second, try to be "affectionate" (act clingy).

00:25:23.330 --> 00:25:24.580
Rose.

00:25:25.500 --> 00:25:27.020
Is there something wrong?

00:25:27.900 --> 00:25:28.700
Not at all.

00:25:29.580 --> 00:25:31.380
I just think it’s an interesting place to visit.

00:25:34.700 --> 00:25:37.420
Please. Can you take me there?

00:25:38.460 --> 00:25:40.100
I want to go with you.

00:25:44.160 --> 00:25:44.960
Deal?

00:26:01.900 --> 00:26:03.500
Din.

00:26:03.930 --> 00:26:05.340
Can I go play in the water?

00:26:10.760 --> 00:26:12.400
You want to get in there?

00:26:13.400 --> 00:26:14.200
Yes.

00:26:15.060 --> 00:26:16.860
This is so refreshing.

00:26:23.700 --> 00:26:24.500
Be careful.

00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:31.530
The water is quite cool.

00:26:35.060 --> 00:26:36.820
That’s great because I’m feeling a little hot.

00:26:38.800 --> 00:26:43.180
[Moddang]: And third, make yourself look “alluring”.

00:26:59.160 --> 00:27:00.900
Can you hold this shirt for me?

00:27:02.160 --> 00:27:03.260
Oh, sure.

00:27:07.600 --> 00:27:08.400
Just a second.

00:27:23.330 --> 00:27:24.900
Be careful there.

00:27:28.740 --> 00:27:30.340
Er…yes.

00:27:35.180 --> 00:27:36.960
The water looks so tempting.

00:27:37.700 --> 00:27:38.900
Wanna get in there together?

00:27:42.560 --> 00:27:43.360
Yes?

00:27:44.500 --> 00:27:46.340
Come on, let’s do it.

00:27:49.660 --> 00:27:50.620
Rose!

00:27:58.660 --> 00:28:00.060
Isn’t it nice?

00:28:00.760 --> 00:28:01.560
Feel good, right?

00:28:02.130 --> 00:28:02.930
Yes.

00:28:05.400 --> 00:28:06.330
Aren’t you cold?

00:28:07.130 --> 00:28:07.930
Yes.

00:28:08.560 --> 00:28:10.140
Are you cold?

00:28:10.400 --> 00:28:12.020
Just…a little.

00:28:12.530 --> 00:28:14.180
Need a hug?

00:28:18.600 --> 00:28:19.500
Fun, isn’t it?

00:28:20.460 --> 00:28:21.660
Oh! It’s cold.

00:28:22.200 --> 00:28:24.220
Sorry, I just splashed your face.

00:28:51.300 --> 00:28:52.580
Awwww!

00:28:52.580 --> 00:28:56.540
Smiling like this, does it mean you already did the 3As technique, Miss?

00:28:57.580 --> 00:29:00.600
Mhm, but I don’t know if it’d work though.

00:29:00.960 --> 00:29:03.130
Did you do your best then, Miss?

00:29:12.760 --> 00:29:15.660
Well…I guess so.

00:29:17.260 --> 00:29:18.330
Now, what’s next?

00:29:18.730 --> 00:29:20.220
Let’s keep going, Miss,

00:29:20.360 --> 00:29:23.930
Next step, we’ll express more possessiveness.

00:29:30.960 --> 00:29:32.500
You’re early, Kaew.

00:29:33.560 --> 00:29:35.260
We have a lot of meetings today.

00:29:35.460 --> 00:29:37.380
I came early in case you might need anything.

00:29:38.060 --> 00:29:39.060
Miss Din…

00:29:40.360 --> 00:29:41.530
Din!

00:29:42.260 --> 00:29:43.060
Please wait.

00:29:45.530 --> 00:29:48.260
I made you sandwiches and orange juice.

00:29:48.600 --> 00:29:50.360
You can eat them while you’re in the car.

00:29:51.360 --> 00:29:52.160
Thank you.

00:29:52.300 --> 00:29:54.100
Hello, Miss Kaew.

00:29:57.300 --> 00:29:58.400
Hello, Miss Rose.

00:30:00.260 --> 00:30:04.460
Will you be home late today?

00:30:04.460 --> 00:30:05.930
I’ll stay up and wait.

00:30:06.730 --> 00:30:09.260
I’m not sure when I’ll finish work.

00:30:09.300 --> 00:30:12.260
But if you’re tired, you can always go to bed first.

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:16.900
What kind of a wife goes to sleep before her hubby?

00:30:17.300 --> 00:30:19.500
I’ll wait until you come back.

00:30:20.330 --> 00:30:23.020
Otherwise, I won’t be able to sleep.

00:30:24.930 --> 00:30:27.400
I’ll hurry home as soon as my work is done.

00:30:29.060 --> 00:30:30.620
Good girl, my baby.

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:39.100
Also,

00:30:39.780 --> 00:30:41.780
if you’re back early,

00:30:41.780 --> 00:30:45.940
I’ll give you a big reward.

00:30:48.380 --> 00:30:50.380
I’ll be waiting.

00:30:54.400 --> 00:30:56.940
[Rose]: I’ll be waiting.

00:30:57.700 --> 00:30:58.660
Miss Din.

00:31:01.800 --> 00:31:02.780
Miss Din.

00:31:04.930 --> 00:31:06.000
Shall we go now?

00:31:08.700 --> 00:31:11.180
You drive then.

00:31:11.860 --> 00:31:12.660
Yes, Miss.

00:31:20.300 --> 00:31:21.500
That’s my girl, Miss.

00:31:21.580 --> 00:31:24.580
As expected of my one and only top class student.

00:31:25.160 --> 00:31:26.400
Am I being too easy?

00:31:27.100 --> 00:31:28.860
You’re her wife, Miss.

00:31:28.860 --> 00:31:31.020
It’s so normal for a wife to do that.

00:31:31.200 --> 00:31:35.380
Besides, I think Miss Din seems to like it a lot.

00:31:35.860 --> 00:31:37.660
But she and I, we’re not…

00:31:38.260 --> 00:31:39.380
Not what?

00:31:41.930 --> 00:31:42.730
Not…

00:31:47.860 --> 00:31:49.900
an expressive type.

00:31:51.160 --> 00:31:53.100
Din is so reserved.

00:31:54.200 --> 00:31:55.460
You know what she’s like.

00:31:56.160 --> 00:31:57.860
If Miss Din is afraid to make her move first,

00:31:58.660 --> 00:32:00.460
why don’t you just start it?

00:32:01.160 --> 00:32:02.780
It’s so easy, Miss.

00:32:03.560 --> 00:32:05.300
What move? Start what?

00:32:06.530 --> 00:32:07.930
Your activity in bed, Miss.

00:32:09.060 --> 00:32:11.140
Do you need me…

00:32:11.140 --> 00:32:12.980
to elaborate more?

00:32:13.460 --> 00:32:14.660
Moddang!

00:32:14.760 --> 00:32:16.730
Like this, Miss. And this.

00:32:16.960 --> 00:32:18.160
That’s enough! Don’t say it.

00:32:18.360 --> 00:32:20.340
Listen to me, Miss.

00:32:20.340 --> 00:32:22.260
- If you want to win in love,
- Stop!

00:32:22.260 --> 00:32:25.460
- you have to make her fall for you both in and out of bed, Miss.
- Stop!

00:32:25.460 --> 00:32:26.140
I don’t want to hear it. No!

00:32:26.160 --> 00:32:28.140
- Trust me, Miss.
- No!

00:32:28.360 --> 00:32:29.160
Stop!

00:32:29.660 --> 00:32:31.000
In and out of bed, Miss!

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:37.380
This client is quite easy to close the deal with.

00:32:38.300 --> 00:32:39.730
It’s all because of you, Miss.

00:32:40.780 --> 00:32:41.600
You’re exaggerating.

00:32:44.530 --> 00:32:48.620
Have you ever thought about finding a new assistant to replace me?

00:32:48.800 --> 00:32:50.360
Why are you asking me that?

00:32:50.930 --> 00:32:52.100
I just feel…

00:32:52.100 --> 00:32:56.820
that maybe Miss Rose isn’t quite pleased to see me going anywhere with you alone.

00:32:58.100 --> 00:32:59.380
Rose?

00:33:00.900 --> 00:33:01.540
Yes.

00:33:01.820 --> 00:33:03.860
I wasn't quite sure at first.

00:33:04.220 --> 00:33:06.900
But after this morning and the day before,

00:33:06.900 --> 00:33:10.580
I’m pretty certain she must love you a lot. That's why she's very possessive of you.

00:33:10.730 --> 00:33:11.530
Possessive of me?

00:33:13.130 --> 00:33:13.860
Yes.

00:33:14.460 --> 00:33:16.620
We often go here and there together.

00:33:16.620 --> 00:33:18.620
It’s understandable if Miss Rose will get jealous.

00:33:21.260 --> 00:33:22.940
I don't think so.

00:33:23.330 --> 00:33:24.820
You probably misunderstood something.

00:33:25.660 --> 00:33:27.740
Things might look peaceful for now.

00:33:27.740 --> 00:33:30.140
But if you transfer me to work on another duty,

00:33:30.330 --> 00:33:32.500
it could help prevent possible problems in the future.

00:33:34.020 --> 00:33:34.980
Kaew.

00:33:35.700 --> 00:33:39.420
You’re my assistant and also my friend.

00:33:39.700 --> 00:33:41.940
Even though I’m now married,

00:33:41.940 --> 00:33:44.220
you can still work with me like before.

00:33:45.160 --> 00:33:45.960
Okay?

00:33:46.660 --> 00:33:47.460
Okay.

00:33:48.930 --> 00:33:51.100
Well then, I’ll go grab some coffee first.

00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:52.530
Would you like anything, Miss?

00:33:52.860 --> 00:33:54.460
No, I’m good. I’ll wait here.

00:33:54.700 --> 00:33:56.100
Okay. I’ll be right back, Miss.

00:34:04.860 --> 00:34:06.560
Does Rose like me for real?

00:34:17.330 --> 00:34:19.199
You’ve called the right person, Sis.

00:34:20.530 --> 00:34:23.130
What’s her reaction? Tell me.

00:34:24.600 --> 00:34:29.300
Well, since that night when I went with Kaew and came home drunk…

00:34:29.929 --> 00:34:33.100
Ha! She’s definitely jealous.

00:34:33.929 --> 00:34:36.159
I think she’s starting to have feelings for you.

00:34:38.760 --> 00:34:40.340
I don’t think so.

00:34:40.659 --> 00:34:42.500
That’s impossible.

00:34:43.460 --> 00:34:45.760
Well then, let’s prove it.

00:34:46.360 --> 00:34:47.600
Let’s test her.

00:34:48.580 --> 00:34:51.620
What do I have to do?

00:34:53.760 --> 00:34:55.260
Just do as I say.

00:34:58.260 --> 00:35:00.730
You’re going to Chiang Mai tomorrow with Miss Kaew again?

00:35:01.160 --> 00:35:01.980
Yes.

00:35:02.220 --> 00:35:05.220
Miss Kanda is our major client.

00:35:05.220 --> 00:35:10.420
She’s holding a grand opening for her hotel, so I should be there to congratulate her.

00:35:10.560 --> 00:35:12.500
The party probably won’t be over until late.

00:35:12.530 --> 00:35:15.460
I’ll have to spend a night there.

00:35:15.740 --> 00:35:17.260
You have to stay over?

00:35:18.100 --> 00:35:19.140
Yes.

00:35:19.460 --> 00:35:21.380
They’ve arranged a room for me.

00:35:21.460 --> 00:35:24.300
I can’t refuse, it would be rude.

00:35:25.930 --> 00:35:29.060
If you’re tired, you can just ask Miss Kaew to drive you home.

00:35:29.060 --> 00:35:31.060
I don’t see why you have to stay over.

00:35:31.060 --> 00:35:33.100
What if Wasu and his father came intruding…

00:35:33.100 --> 00:35:35.860
while I’m here alone?

00:35:35.860 --> 00:35:38.900
What should I do then? I’m scared.

00:35:39.700 --> 00:35:42.060
Please don’t be scared.

00:35:42.660 --> 00:35:45.180
I already asked Lom to send someone to keep watch.

00:35:45.560 --> 00:35:46.580
But I…

00:35:49.060 --> 00:35:50.140
I…

00:35:51.560 --> 00:35:54.460
You what, Rose?

00:35:57.260 --> 00:35:58.060
Whatever.

00:35:59.500 --> 00:36:01.330
I’m going to Chiang Mai with you.

00:36:01.860 --> 00:36:02.980
Eh?

00:36:03.930 --> 00:36:05.360
To make it more believable.

00:36:05.800 --> 00:36:07.060
You just got married.

00:36:08.000 --> 00:36:10.220
Surely, you should introduce your wife to everyone.

00:36:10.560 --> 00:36:12.540
If you keep showing up with your assistant,

00:36:12.540 --> 00:36:13.980
people might be getting the wrong idea.

00:36:14.330 --> 00:36:15.900
And our plan would be exposed.

00:36:18.130 --> 00:36:23.300
I see. You’re just afraid our plan would be exposed, aren’t you?

00:36:24.300 --> 00:36:27.540
Yes. We have to play along and do our best.

00:36:28.620 --> 00:36:34.100
Let’s say–from now on–no matter where you go, I’ll go with you.

00:36:36.330 --> 00:36:39.300
I’d better go pack my dress then.

00:36:50.130 --> 00:36:53.060
See? I told you.

00:36:53.130 --> 00:36:55.560
She’s starting to become possessive of her meat.

00:36:56.660 --> 00:36:58.260
Did you just call me ‘meat’?

00:36:58.700 --> 00:37:01.560
That’s not what I meant. Geez!

00:37:02.330 --> 00:37:06.740
What I meant is, Rose clearly tries to get between you and Miss Kaew.

00:37:08.800 --> 00:37:10.900
Can that even prove anything?

00:37:11.530 --> 00:37:16.100
Seriously! It’s so obvious she likes you.

00:37:16.700 --> 00:37:20.660
By the way, will that girl–Gun–who has a crush on you be there too?

00:37:20.660 --> 00:37:24.420
If so, you should use her to make Rose jealous.

00:37:24.660 --> 00:37:27.600
Then just wait and see how Rose will react.

00:37:36.860 --> 00:37:38.260
Hello, Miss Kanda.

00:37:38.600 --> 00:37:39.400
Hello.

00:37:39.960 --> 00:37:40.760
Congratulations.

00:37:41.300 --> 00:37:42.100
Thank you.

00:37:42.260 --> 00:37:43.060
I hope you’ve been doing well.

00:37:43.400 --> 00:37:44.260
Yes, thank you.

00:37:44.600 --> 00:37:47.860
Who do you have here? She isn’t Miss Kaew, is she?

00:37:48.000 --> 00:37:50.060
- This is Rose, my…
- My lovely Din!

00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:52.800
Gun.

00:37:55.130 --> 00:37:56.700
It’s been a long time.

00:37:57.100 --> 00:37:58.860
I miss you so much.

00:37:59.900 --> 00:38:01.730
She just came back from abroad.

00:38:02.130 --> 00:38:05.020
And also brought with her a fresh degree for her mother.

00:38:05.400 --> 00:38:06.820
Congratulations.

00:38:08.600 --> 00:38:11.260
Do you have a new assistant?

00:38:16.000 --> 00:38:18.740
Miss Kanda. Gun.

00:38:19.100 --> 00:38:22.660
This is Rose, my wife.

00:38:23.300 --> 00:38:25.220
This girl is your wife?

00:38:25.620 --> 00:38:27.340
Since when did you get married?

00:38:27.340 --> 00:38:29.060
I have no idea.

00:38:34.130 --> 00:38:37.740
Hello, Miss Kanda. Hello, Miss Gun.

00:38:45.960 --> 00:38:48.130
Miss Kanda, this way please.

00:39:07.330 --> 00:39:08.820
Gun and I…

00:39:09.140 --> 00:39:12.580
have known each other since when she was in high school.

00:39:12.900 --> 00:39:15.540
I only see her as a younger sister.

00:39:15.980 --> 00:39:20.340
As for Kaew, I only think of her as a close friend.

00:39:21.200 --> 00:39:23.140
Why are you telling me this?

00:39:23.400 --> 00:39:25.180
I didn't ask.

00:39:26.020 --> 00:39:30.340
I just think it’s something my wife should know.

00:39:30.760 --> 00:39:32.860
At first, I thought…

00:39:32.860 --> 00:39:35.100
you only get jealous when I’m with Kaew.

00:39:35.100 --> 00:39:39.180
But today, it seems you’re also jealous of Gun.

00:39:40.160 --> 00:39:42.060
You’re getting a wrong idea.

00:39:42.620 --> 00:39:45.820
I’ve never been jealous of you with any other women.

00:39:46.330 --> 00:39:47.130
Really?

00:39:47.930 --> 00:39:48.780
Yes.

00:39:48.780 --> 00:39:52.220
I’m just doing my job as your fake wife.

00:39:52.220 --> 00:39:55.020
You see, I have to show them…

00:39:55.330 --> 00:39:59.700
that I’m possessive when other women get near you.

00:39:59.700 --> 00:40:02.420
It’s all just for show.

00:40:03.200 --> 00:40:06.600
I see. Just for show.

00:40:08.300 --> 00:40:11.620
Yes, because we’re not married for real, right?

00:40:11.620 --> 00:40:14.140
Otherwise, why would I be possessive of you?

00:40:15.000 --> 00:40:17.180
I’m doing a great job, aren’t I?

00:40:18.260 --> 00:40:19.660
Superb indeed.

00:40:20.700 --> 00:40:22.100
Right?

00:40:22.160 --> 00:40:24.900
I even got you to believe that I was really possessive of you.

00:40:25.400 --> 00:40:26.730
I’m so good at this.

00:40:29.330 --> 00:40:30.130
Din.

00:40:32.160 --> 00:40:32.960
There you are.

00:40:33.360 --> 00:40:34.860
My mother is looking for you.

00:40:35.100 --> 00:40:37.180
She wants to introduce you to her friends.

00:40:42.930 --> 00:40:45.340
Go on, Babe.

00:40:45.340 --> 00:40:47.220
Don’t worry about me.

00:40:52.730 --> 00:40:55.360
Don’t worry, I’ll keep her company while you’re away.

00:40:57.860 --> 00:40:59.220
Take care of her for me then.

00:40:59.220 --> 00:40:59.860
Yes.

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:09.160
Do you usually drink?

00:41:10.200 --> 00:41:11.000
Yes.

00:41:24.330 --> 00:41:28.260
When we have a party, I often come to drink with Din like this.

00:41:30.800 --> 00:41:33.620
But usually, she doesn’t drink.

00:41:34.260 --> 00:41:36.540
She said it’s useless.

00:41:41.500 --> 00:41:43.900
I can’t believe Din is already married.

00:41:45.820 --> 00:41:48.900
I know it’s hard to believe but I’m afraid you’ll have to accept it.

00:41:49.460 --> 00:41:54.500
That Din and I are now married.

00:41:55.930 --> 00:41:58.530
How long have you been together?

00:41:59.300 --> 00:42:00.360
I’ve never heard about you before.

00:42:02.130 --> 00:42:04.130
We’ve known each other since very little.

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:06.940
Probably even before you were born.

00:42:08.130 --> 00:42:11.140
Our farms are right next to each other.

00:42:12.000 --> 00:42:13.000
What about you?

00:42:15.360 --> 00:42:17.160
I’ve known her for 5-6 years now.

00:42:22.160 --> 00:42:24.600
At first, I thought Din would surely fall for Miss Kaew…

00:42:25.800 --> 00:42:27.800
since they’re always together.

00:42:29.400 --> 00:42:32.160
She always comes here with her.

00:43:07.460 --> 00:43:09.380
I need to use the restroom.

00:43:10.860 --> 00:43:13.540
Mhm, bye.

00:43:31.560 --> 00:43:32.660
Hey, pretty.

00:43:33.700 --> 00:43:35.100
Where are you going?

00:43:35.900 --> 00:43:37.860
Do you need a hand?

00:43:41.200 --> 00:43:42.200
Are you talking to me?

00:43:42.760 --> 00:43:44.860
Yes, I’m talking to you.

00:43:51.060 --> 00:43:52.140
Thank you.

00:43:52.140 --> 00:43:55.540
But l’d rather you let it be my job to take care of my wife.

00:43:55.540 --> 00:43:57.220
No need to bother someone else.

00:44:01.330 --> 00:44:02.130
Rose.

00:44:03.660 --> 00:44:06.760
I’m sorry I left you alone.

00:44:10.660 --> 00:44:11.760
You need the loo, right?

00:44:13.500 --> 00:44:14.400
Let me help.

00:44:18.020 --> 00:44:19.380
Be careful.

00:44:23.700 --> 00:44:26.220
Watch your steps.

00:44:26.700 --> 00:44:29.560
Why is it taking so long? I’m tired.

00:44:31.330 --> 00:44:32.740
Do you want me to carry you?

00:44:33.300 --> 00:44:37.620
Carry me? I’m not a child anymore.

00:44:37.620 --> 00:44:39.220
Okay. Be careful.

00:44:40.180 --> 00:44:44.060
Hang on.

00:44:45.260 --> 00:44:46.180
Easy there.

00:44:50.900 --> 00:44:52.340
Rose.

00:44:53.500 --> 00:44:55.060
What are you doing?

00:45:01.700 --> 00:45:05.500
What are you doing, Rose?

00:45:10.660 --> 00:45:11.980
Why?

00:45:14.200 --> 00:45:15.000
Rose.

00:45:40.060 --> 00:45:41.500
Be a good girl.

00:45:58.160 --> 00:46:02.340
You’re such a softie, do you know that?

00:46:03.700 --> 00:46:04.980
Me?

00:46:06.800 --> 00:46:07.600
Yes.

00:46:16.160 --> 00:46:19.580
Why does everyone want to approach you?

00:46:22.930 --> 00:46:24.700
You already have a wife.

00:47:12.400 --> 00:47:18.100
If anything happens, let’s just say it’s because I’m drunk.

00:50:28.930 --> 00:50:30.820
Are you awake, Rose?

00:50:33.600 --> 00:50:36.160
You were so drunk last night, do you know that?

00:50:37.530 --> 00:50:39.160
I can’t remember anything.

00:50:41.700 --> 00:50:45.220
I took you back to our room…

00:50:45.220 --> 00:50:47.340
Then you just fell asleep until now.

00:50:57.700 --> 00:51:02.820
I swear I didn't take any advantage of you while you were drunk last night.

00:51:03.460 --> 00:51:05.300
So, don’t worry.

00:51:08.000 --> 00:51:12.100
I never thought you’d do anything like that anyway.

00:51:13.530 --> 00:51:15.930
That’s why I agreed to marry you.

00:51:18.530 --> 00:51:19.330
I see.

00:51:26.200 --> 00:51:31.340
So, when are we leaving? I’ll go get myself ready.

00:51:32.060 --> 00:51:33.930
We can leave whenever you want.

00:51:34.860 --> 00:51:36.940
You’re pampering me again.

00:51:37.860 --> 00:51:41.400
Who else could I possibly pamper if not you?

00:51:43.330 --> 00:51:47.460
Absolutely no one. Not even Miss Gun or Miss Kaew.

00:51:49.400 --> 00:51:52.800
Are you playing the role of a jealous wife now?

00:51:53.930 --> 00:51:55.820
You certainly pulled it off.

00:51:55.820 --> 00:51:57.700
If you hadn’t told me first,

00:51:58.060 --> 00:52:00.260
I would’ve really believed it was true.

00:52:01.560 --> 00:52:05.620
Do you maybe want to roleplay…

00:52:06.060 --> 00:52:08.180
a morning kiss scenario?

00:52:29.800 --> 00:52:32.130
Do you want to stop by anywhere before we go home?

00:52:34.400 --> 00:52:35.930
I’d like to go visit my dad.

00:52:36.530 --> 00:52:39.460
I haven’t been able to see him since after the wedding.

00:52:41.760 --> 00:52:42.560
Sure.

00:53:12.800 --> 00:53:14.860
I’m here to see you, Dad.

00:53:15.540 --> 00:53:18.380
I’m sorry I didn’t come earlier.

00:53:18.940 --> 00:53:20.580
Please don’t be mad at me.

00:53:21.500 --> 00:53:24.820
I think Uncle can hear you.

00:53:26.100 --> 00:53:29.460
Look at his face, it seems a lot better than last time.

00:53:30.730 --> 00:53:31.530
Really?

00:53:32.300 --> 00:53:33.100
Yes.

00:53:35.600 --> 00:53:39.300
You stay with Uncle first. I’ll go talk to the doctor…

00:53:39.300 --> 00:53:42.540
if there might be any way to make him recover faster.

00:53:43.600 --> 00:53:44.900
Thank you.

00:54:01.860 --> 00:54:04.730
Din is taking such great care of me, Dad.

00:54:06.500 --> 00:54:07.760
Please don’t worry.

00:54:09.960 --> 00:54:12.220
You have chosen the right person.

00:54:33.930 --> 00:54:35.380
Dad.

00:54:45.200 --> 00:54:46.540
Dad!

00:55:19.130 --> 00:55:20.900
[Next Episode]
I’ll sleep at the office tonight.

00:55:21.600 --> 00:55:23.260
[Din]: I don’t want to bother Rose.

00:55:23.900 --> 00:55:28.260
[Wasu]: That brat had a falling-out with Rose and had to go sleep in the office?

00:55:29.700 --> 00:55:33.160
[Moddang]: You should go apologize to Miss Din. Make it sweet and gentle, Miss.

00:55:34.600 --> 00:55:35.540
[Rose]: Moddang.

00:55:35.860 --> 00:55:36.700
Let’s go.

00:55:36.900 --> 00:55:39.530
Wait, Miss. You’re getting jealous again.

00:55:40.800 --> 00:55:43.460
Lom, give me some advice.

00:55:43.460 --> 00:55:46.500
There are many ways to make girls forgive you.

00:55:47.100 --> 00:55:51.000
[Lom]: But if she’s really mad, you might have to make it a little extravaganza.

00:55:51.760 --> 00:55:52.560
[Fai]: Holy moly!

00:55:54.530 --> 00:55:56.260
Are we in the Himmapan forest?

00:55:56.700 --> 00:55:57.900
What? It’s nice.

00:56:13.020 --> 00:56:16.820
♫ Your touch burns a flame so bright,♫

00:56:16.820 --> 00:56:20.180
♫Your warm embrace♫

00:56:21.500 --> 00:56:27.700
♫Cools me down like ocean waves♫

00:56:28.740 --> 00:56:35.020
♫A breeze so light, makes me wanna fly away♫

00:56:35.020 --> 00:56:42.220
♫You keep me grounded, peaceful, and safe♫

00:56:42.220 --> 00:56:48.700
♫Take my hand and just believe♫

00:56:49.060 --> 00:56:53.340
♫I will stay right here beside you♫

00:56:53.340 --> 00:56:56.340
♫And get through what will be♫

00:56:56.340 --> 00:57:02.460
♫Night and day, In my arms, You and me♫

00:57:02.460 --> 00:57:08.380
♫With our love and destiny♫

00:57:12.060 --> 00:57:21.580
♫From here and now I’ll be with you♫

00:57:21.580 --> 00:57:22.820
[North Star Entertainment]

00:57:23.900 --> 00:57:34.780
[The Earth]